YamlPropertySourceFactory is a class implemented by Baeldung in this guide: 
 [@PropertySource with YAML Files in Spring Boot][1]


    public class YamlPropertySourceFactory implements PropertySourceFactory {
    
    	@Override
    	public PropertySource&lt;?&gt; createPropertySource(String name, EncodedResource resource) throws IOException {
    		YamlPropertiesFactoryBean factory = new YamlPropertiesFactoryBean();
    		factory.setResources(resource.getResource());
    
    		Properties properties = factory.getObject();
    
    		return new PropertiesPropertySource(resource.getResource().getFilename(), properties);
    	}
    
    }

